{"tid":1188860,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子羈留上水警署時昏迷 送院搶救不治","createTime":"2019-06-06T13:57:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T15:01:45.000Z","uid":18213,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e214de95573740fee3c2e037e4a1d51eb48d0348","tid":1188860,"uid":18213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T13:57:17.000Z","msg":"一名在上水警署扣押的男疑犯今日凌晨在羈留室昏迷，送院搶救後不治！凌晨零時許，一名羈留於警署的46歲姓王男子，被警員發現他昏迷不醒，身旁有嘔吐物，警員見狀立即替他進行急救，然後由救護車送往北區醫院治理，可惜最終不治。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，疑犯有吸毒習慣，曾有多宗涉及販毒及藏毒的案底，周二（4日）他在上水石湖墟一唐樓單位以涉嫌販毒被警方拘捕，並於他身上撿獲少量冰毒及廿多粒海洛英。疑犯被捕後一直被扣押在上水警署，早前曾被押往美沙酮中心，原定今日會被押送到粉嶺法院應訊，惟至今日凌晨被警員發現昏迷在羈留室。<br />\n<br />\n據知，疑犯身上沒有自殺傾向，身上亦無明顯傷痕，警員經初步調查相信事件並無可疑，死因有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190606/59686051\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190606%2F59686051&d=M59wMjr1KB2wSFKn0iQ%2BgvZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=2332fcce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190606%2F59686051&h=b46eb81a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190606/59686051</a>"},{"pid":"bbd81bc8f945279561a03355d693b42ad93001a2","tid":1188860,"uid":157362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T13:58:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c95656bdaae27beb3d9613620ac1545cf54703e1","tid":1188860,"uid":5499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T13:58:10.000Z","msg":"隔住本電話簿係咪驗唔到傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e6837d6d0075715d63e85d37f1c2baced72e40d","tid":1188860,"uid":18213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T14:05:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92742a4f3cf67374be8b91ba3d1bd726681f54c2","tid":1188860,"uid":50790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited